    "The software package ATHENA, developed by Kim et al. [87] (Fig.",
    "2a), incorporated this data into grammatical evolution neural networks.",
    "Here, over several iterations, sets of neural networks with varying parameters are constructed, and the best-performing networks are combined in the following iteration until the best solution is reached.",
